data.description: Spacious, move-in ready single-family home with deepwater dockage and direct ocean access! Current boat in the boat slip is 45'.  This concrete fortress is ready for you and your vessel, offering you a gateway to the world's best fishing and diving, right in your backyard. Built to perfection in 2009, this home features high vaulted ceilings, beautiful travertine flooring throughout, a large gourmet kitchen, spacious walk-in closets, and the security of all impact windows and doors. The concrete roof not only provides durability but also offers a rooftop deck with stunning views. Of course, deep water dockage is at your disposal. You will enjoy the convenience with a short distance to various bars and restaurants, the Pilot House Marina for bait and fuel, and access to the freshest seafood from Key Largo's fisheries. Start your day with a visit to Key Largo Park just around the corner, offering Pickleball, tennis, swimming, and more. Don't miss out on this opportunity. Call today for appointment!
